    "Return covariance estimate.",
    "There are many ways to estimate the covariance matrix, with or without a factor model.",
    "Approaches that work well in practice include the exponentially weighted moving average (EWMA) [OS96], dynamic conditional correlation (DCC) [Eng02], and iterated EWMA [BB22].",
